bit trickier. If I do 4 times x I have 4x. But I don't need one of them, I need

00:00:19.497 --> 00:00:24.216
two. So I'm going to have 2 times my first term and my second term. The same is

00:00:24.216 --> 00:00:29.213
true down here. I don't just have one 3x, I have two. So I'm going to have the

00:00:29.213 --> 00:00:34.129
first term times the second term, times 2. So here's the first term, a, times

